esource/Chelsea_F.C.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1985}, {\"ngram\": \"two players\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2058}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You have to know that it's not easy to find yourself in a situation where you have to go and ask a certain club for permission to be able to take their players when you actually can not ask for anything since they are within their right not to send since it's not a FIFA date,' Henry said when announcing his provisional squad for the competition.\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2341, \"end\": 2345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 0.998934326489796, \"rank\": 0.001066810372983316, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a situation\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2142}, {\"ngram\": \"a certain club\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2186}, {\"ngram\": \"permission\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"their players\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2234}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2277}, {\"ngram\": \"their right\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2311}, {\"ngram\": \"Henry\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"his provisional squad\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2401}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'When it's already a FIFA date it's hard, so there you go, we are trying to find ways to have certain players and believe me it's not easy,' Henry said after unveiling his provisional squad.\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2445, \"end\": 2449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 0.998934326489796, \"rank\": 0.001066810372983316, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbped